special_powers.name: CHANGING THE WORLD: ISOLATE AND CONTAIN
special_powers.description: Opposing characters adjacent to two or more friendly characters with the S.H.I.E.L.D. keyword can't use Willpower, Telekinesis, or the Carry ability.

special_powers.name: SUBERTING S.H.I.E.L.D.'S COMMAND STRUCTURE
special_powers.description: Adjacent friendly characters with the S.H.I.E.L.D. keyword can use Leadership, but remove an action token from a higher point character with the S.H.I.E.L.D. keyword instead.

special_powers.name: INVADE YOUR TERRITORY
special_powers.description: Namor ignores opposing Barrier and Smoke Cloud markers for movement purposes and removes them from the game when moving through them.

special_powers.name: ...AND LEAVE BEHIND A BIT OF MINE
special_powers.description: When Namor or another friendly character uses the "Invade Your Territory" trait, after actions resolve, you may place a water terrain marker in any of the squares from which a Barrier or Smoke Cloud marker was removed.

special_powers.name: MASTER OF UNDERSEA TRAVEL
special_powers.description: If Namor occupies a square of water terrain and has 0 or 1 action tokens, give Namor a free action to place him in another square of water terrain within 6 squares.

special_powers.name: REVEALING ALL THE SECRETS
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, choose a copyable team ability that an opposing character within range and line of fire can use. Until your next turn, Spider-Woman can use this team ability and that character can't use this team ability.

special_powers.name: WEB GLIDERS
special_powers.description: Spider-Woman can use Leap/Climb and Sidestep. Once per turn, when Spider-Woman is given a move action and moves 4 squares or less, after actions resolve she can make a close or ranged combat attack as a free action.

special_powers.name: COSMIC ASSASSIN, GUARDIAN OF EARTH
special_powers.description: Nick Fury can use Shape Change. When Nick Fury targets only the highest point opposing character with an attack, modify his attack and damage values by +1 and he deals penetrating damage.

special_powers.name: WATCHER'S EYES TO SEE SECRETS
special_powers.description: Nick Fury can use Probability Control. Give Nick Fury a free action and choose a power that an opposing character within range and line of fire can use. That character can't use that power until your next turn.

name: Madame Hydra
real_name: Contessa Valentina Allegra de la Fontaine

special_powers.name: HYDRA'S REACH IS NEVER-ENDING
special_powers.description: When Madame Hydra takes damage from an attack, after actions resolve you may choose one character adjacent to the attacker and deal them 1 penetrating damage and give them 1 action token.

special_powers.name: BEAUTY WITH A BLACK HEART
special_powers.description: Madame Hydra heals 1 damage each time another friendly character that shares a keyword with her is KO'd.

special_powers.name: WE ARE AMONG YOU
special_powers.description: Madame Hydra can use Poison. When she uses Poison, she deals penetrating damage to characters with the S.H.I.E.L.D. keyword.

special_powers.name: I KNOW ALL YOUR SECRETS
special_powers.description: Madame Hydra can use Outwit and Shape Change. Opposing characters within range and line of fire that use Outwit or Perplex must be given a power action instead of a free action to use it.

special_powers.name: PSYCHIC ENERGIES OF MIND-SLAVES
special_powers.description: When Golden Claw hits an opposing character, place a Mind-Slave token on that character's card. Characters with one or more Mind-Slave tokens modify their combat values by -1 when targeting Golden Claw with an attack. Remove one of his Mind-Slave tokens from an opponent's card to modify Golden Claw's combat values by +1 until your next turn.

special_powers.name: ID PARALYZER
special_powers.description: Golden Claw can use Mind Control. When he does, Golden Claw's line of fire isn't blocked when targeting an opposing character with a Mind-Slave token.

special_powers.name: ILLUSIONARY DISGUISE
special_powers.description: Golden Claw can use Probability Control and Shape Change. When he uses Shape Change, he succeeds on a result of 4-6 if targeted by a non-adjacent character.

special_powers.name: NIGHT AND DAY
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, an opponent chooses Night -or- Day. If they choose Night, modify Nighthawk's combat values by +1. If they choose Day, modify the defense values of all characters by -1 unless they occupy hindering terrain or are friendly to Nighthawk.

special_powers.name: PUSHING THE DEFENDERS TO BE MORE PROACTIVE
special_powers.description: Nighthawk and friendly characters that share a keyword with him may replace their attack value with the unmodified attack value of an adjacent friendly character sharing that same keyword.

special_powers.name: SHIELDED WINGS
special_powers.description: Nighthawk can use Energy Shield/Deflection, Toughness, and Willpower.

special_powers.name: THE PEOPLE MUST THINK FOR THEMSELVES
special_powers.description: Friendly characters can't be targeted by Mind Control. Opposing characters' combat values can't be increased unless they are adjacent to Nighthawk.

special_powers.name: NIGHT GLIDING
special_powers.description: Nighthawk can use Charge, Stealth, and the Flight ability.

special_powers.name: PRESIDENT OF THE UNITED STATES (OF EARTH-712)
special_powers.description: Nighthawk can use Energy Shield/Deflection and Shape Change. When he uses Shape Change, increase the result by +1 for each adjacent friendly character.

special_powers.name: HYDRA'S REACH IS WORLDWIDE
special_powers.description: When Baron Strucker takes damage from an attack and actions resolve, deal 1 penetrating damage to the attacker and each opposing character within 2 squares of the attacker.

special_powers.name: RUTHLESSLY PURSUING HYDRA'S GOALS
special_powers.description: Each time another friendly character with the Hydra keyword is KO'd by an opposing character, modify the combat values of all friendly characters with the Hydra keyword by +1 until the end of your next turn.

special_powers.name: SATAN CLAW SLASH
special_powers.description: Baron Strucker can use Blades/Claws/Fangs and Exploit Weakness.

special_powers.name: HYDRA'S TRUE LEADER
special_powers.description: Baron Strucker can use Leadership and Perplex.

special_powers.name: PERSONAL CRAFT: HAWKEYE
special_powers.description: A themed team may include Avengers Sky-Cycle and is still a themed team as long as a character named Hawkeye is on your force.

special_powers.name: UNBELIEVABLE UPSIDE-DOWN SHOT
special_powers.description: When Avengers Sky-Cycle makes an attack, you may modify its attack value by +2. If you do and actions resolve, roll a d6 that can't be rerolled and on a result of 1, place the pilot in an adjacent square, dealing it and all passengers 2 unavoidable damage.

special_powers.name: PERSONAL CRAFT: CAPTAIN AMERICA
special_powers.description: A themed team may include Captain America's Motorcycle and is still a themed team as long as a character named Captain America is on your force.

special_powers.name: JUMP IT!
special_powers.description: Captain America's Motorcycle can use Improved Movement: Elevated. If Captain America's Motorcycle moves and crosses at least one edge of elevated terrain, adjacent opposing characters modify their defense value -1 this turn.

special_powers.name: RAM
special_powers.description: Give Captain America's Motorcycle a move action to use Improved Movement: Characters and move along a direct path. After actions resolve, make a close combat attack targeting all opposing characters whose squares were moved through. Each hit character is dealt this printed damage value and then deal Captain America's Motorcycle 1 unavoidable damage for each hit character.

special_powers.name: PERSONAL CRAFT: NICK FURY
special_powers.description: A themed team may include S.H.I.E.L.D. Space Rig and is still a themed team as long as a character named Nick Fury is on your force.

special_powers.name: SUB-ORBITAL LIFT
special_powers.description: S.H.I.E.L.D. Space Rig can use Energy Shield/Deflection. If S.H.I.E.L.D. Space Rig has two action tokens, it can't be the target of close combat attacks.

special_powers.name: PERSONAL CRAFT: KANG
special_powers.description: A themed team may include Kang's Time Chair and is still a themed team as long as a character named Kang or Kang the Conqueror is on your force.

special_powers.name: AUTOPILOT
special_powers.description: This vehicle may be given actions without a pilot. When it doesn't have a pilot and an action resolves in which it made an attack, deal it one unavoidable damage.

special_powers.name: VIEW THE TIMELINES FROM ON HIGH
special_powers.description: Kang's Time Chair can use Probability Control. Each time an opposing character within range and line of fire uses Probability Control, Kang's Time Chair may immediately use Probability Control even if it has already used it this turn.

special_powers.name: PERSONAL CRAFT: THANOS
special_powers.description: A themed team may include Thanos Throne and is still a themed team as long as a character named Thanos is on your force.

special_powers.name: LESSER BEINGS ARE INCINERATED
special_powers.description: Thanos Throne can only be piloted by characters 100 points or more.

special_powers.name: AUTOPILOT
special_powers.description: This vehicle may be given actions without a pilot. When it doesn't have a pilot and an action resolves during which it made an attack, deal it 1 unavoidable damage.

special_powers.name: YOUR NEW MASTER DEMANDS HOMAGE
special_powers.description: Give Thanos Throne a power action if it has a pilot. For each opposing character within 2 squares with 0 or 1 action tokens, that character's controller chooses: Give that character an action token or deal that character 2 penetrating damage.

special_powers.name: DEPARTMENT X
special_powers.description: Friendly characters with a higher point value and the scientist keyword may use Mind Control, but only to target Winter Soldier.

special_powers.name: TAKE A HIT AND MINDLESSLY KEEP GOING
special_powers.description: Winter Soldier can use Invulnerability and Willpower.

special_powers.name: BEEN WAITING FOR THIS SHOT ALL MORNING
special_powers.description: Winter Soldier can use Ranged Combat Expert and Improved Targeting: Characters. When he uses Ranged Combat Expert, he may instead choose a direction and target all opposing characters along that direct line.

special_powers.name: EFFECT
special_powers.description: This character can use Invulnerability.

special_powers.name: EFFECT
special_powers.description: This character can use Toughness and the Flight ability.

special_powers.name: EFFECT
special_powers.description: This character can use Toughness and its attacks generate knock back.

special_powers.name: EFFECT
special_powers.description: This character can use Energy Explosion and has a minimum range value of 6.

special_powers.name: EFFECT
special_powers.description: This character can use Exploit Weakness.

special_powers.name: ASSEMBLING THE HULKBUSTER
special_powers.description: To play NFAOS #G001 Hulkbuster Mark II, you must have all 5 Hulkbuster Mark II pieces NFAOS #A001 - NFAOS #A005 attached. To start on the 500 or 300 point starting line, you must attach NFAOS #053 Iron Man by placing him on this card. You don't pay the point cost for any of these attachments and they can't be added separately to your force.

special_powers.name: MODULAR DESIGN
special_powers.description: When Hulkbuster Mark II is KO'ed, place the 5 attached Hulkbuster Mark II pieces on the map in different squares adjacent to or in the squares Hulkbuster Mark II last occupied. If you started the game with NFAOS #053 Iron Man, place him adjacent to or in one of the squares Hulkbuster Mark II last occupied on his 50 point starting line. This ability can't be ignored.

special_powers.name: TITANIC PUNCH
special_powers.description: When Hulkbuster Mark II hits an adjacent opposing character with a critical hit, knock that character back until it hits the edge of the map, destroying all blocking terrain along the path. After actions resolve, deal that character damage equal to the number of walls and squares of blocking terrain destroyed in this way.

special_powers.name: EVACUATE THE AREA!
special_powers.description: Hulkbuster Mark II can use Charge and Quake. Give Hulkbuster Mark II a move action and after it resolves, he can use Quake as a free action.

special_powers.name: BUILT TO WITHSTAND HULK'S RAGE
special_powers.description: Hulkbuster Mark II can use Impervious. If he would take more than 2 damage at once, he takes 2 damage instead. This power can't be countered or ignored.

special_powers.name: Inspiration
special_powers.description: Can use Exploit Weakness.

special_powers.name: Inspiration
special_powers.description: Can use Barrier and Smoke Cloud and Stealth.

special_powers.name: Inspiration
special_powers.description: Modify defense value by +1.

special_powers.name: Inspiration
special_powers.description: Can use Telekinesis.

special_powers.name: Inspiration
special_powers.description: Can use Force Blast and Quake.

special_powers.name: Inspiration
special_powers.description: Modify attack value by +1.

special_powers.name: Inspiration
special_powers.description: Character can use the S.H.I.E.L.D. team ability. Modify attack value by +1 when making a ranged combat attack.

special_powers.name: Inspiration
special_powers.description: Character can use the S.H.I.E.L.D. team ability. Modify speed value by +1.

special_powers.name: Inspiration
special_powers.description: Opposing characters can't use Barrier or Smoke Cloud or Stealth.

special_powers.name: Inspiration
special_powers.description: Modify damage value by +1.

special_powers.name: Inspiration
special_powers.description: Modify range value by +1. Ignore opposing Shape Change when attacking.

special_powers.name: Inspiration
special_powers.description: Can use Empower when indoors. Can use Enhancement when outdoors.

special_powers.name: Inspiration
special_powers.description: Can use Poison.

special_powers.name: Inspiration
special_powers.description: Can use Plasticity. Ignore opposing Super Senses when attacking.

special_powers.name: Inspiration
special_powers.description: Can use Shape Change.
